title: THEODORA DOUBLE TRILLION RING, SILVER

Crafted from trillion cut lab-grown white sapphires set in sterling silver or 14K white gold, the Theodora ring is designed to be effortlessly stacked. Discover the entire Theodora Ring Collection here.

Due to increased order volume during the holiday season, please place your order by November 1st for guaranteed delivery before December 25th. Orders placed after this date cannot be guaranteed to arrive in time for the holidays. 
Custom styles can only be returned for store credit.
